title: Kristi Noem cast as Cruella de Vil in Newsom Halloween message
description: (KRON) -- U.S. Department of Homeland Security Secretary Kristi Noem was cast as Disney villain Cruella de Ville in a Halloween message from California Gov. Gavin Newsom. In an official release from the governor's office, he accused Noem of "terrifying kids" and taking "pleasure in tearing families apart -- deporting hardworking, tax-paying people contributing to [...]

title: The British government ‘must recognise hydrogen’, says Hyundai
description: Hydrogen vehicles have long been a future promise, but with only two public refuelling stations in the UK, Hyundai is urging the government to go further

title: G7 says it's 'serious' about confronting China's critical mineral dominance
description: The G7 announced two dozen new projects Friday aimed at reducing China's dominance of critical mineral supply chains, as Canada's energy minister vowed the alliance was "serious" about reforming the global market.
